$$
\text {

options:
A. } \vec{u}=\left(\left|\begin{array}{cc}
y_{2} & z_{2} \\
y_{1} & z_{1}
\end{array}\right| ;\left|\begin{array}{cc}
z_{2} & x_{2} \\
z_{1} & x_{1}
\end{array}\right| ;\left|\begin{array}{cc}
x_{2} & y_{2} \\
x_{1} & y_{1}
\end{array}\right|\right)
$$

